    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just that the clinic is so far away and it's gonna cost me a ton if i go in for an urgent visit. i'm pretty sure it's just dehydration. if i just take like a couple of extra salt tablets and drink a whole extra liter of water tonight, wouldn't that basically do the same thing as a blood test for checking the balance? i just need a definite yes or no so i can stop feeling sick.",
